"_blank"&gt;The Legend of zelda: Twilight princess - Sacred grove&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Horse ride&lt;br&gt;     &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whHZxFLT7a0" target="_blank"&gt;The legend of zelda: A link to the past - Hyrule field&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;I had to do a bit of editing on some tracks, particularly on the large bosses, since there are 2 phases.</description>
