    <item>
      <title>Dragon Princess Armor</title>
      <author>-alpha-</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/614241</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/614241#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">6cf620e1845802759de42c91578c780a1ed415a0</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Sep 2025 17:35:29 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0ea282b20e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68aee942384e4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a4b115baef5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0eaf2b43df.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0eaf58af45.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68a0f04539a97.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b87b4a694bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b87b4da053d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68b87b4d9cc94.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Dragon Princess&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Horn colors changes with dyes&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a &lt;strong data-start="314" data-end="338"&gt;standalone armor set&lt;/strong&gt; that works on Link’s &lt;strong data-start="360" data-end="383"&gt;original model. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully upgradeable and dyeable!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compatible with most Link replacement mods and animations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Design: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The armor set is based off Zelda's model, Yamato's hair (One Piece), Zonai and Dragon Armor, and Master Sword concept art. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Upgrades&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 1 (Light Dragon): Gloom resistance + Zonai efficiency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 2 (Naydra): Cold resistance + Ice attack charge power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 3 (Dinraal): Hot and Flame resistance + Fire charge attack power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level 4 (Farosh): Lightning resistance + Lightning immunity + Lightning attack charge power&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Light Dragon Master Sword:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Standalone master sword, base dmg 60, durability x3, and heal on hit&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master Sword cutscene uses the new Light Dragon model&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Location:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Armor and sword can be obtained in &lt;strong data-start="1166" data-end="1189"&gt;Zelda’s Secret Well&lt;/strong&gt; (Hateno Village)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Optional:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2173" data-end="2187"&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/523154"&gt;Femme Hero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (female voice mod) — by &lt;em data-start="2212" data-end="2225"&gt;SpaceGeorge &amp; &lt;/em&gt;Adeline Chetail&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2230" data-end="2245"&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/469131"&gt;Femboy Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (female animation mod) — by &lt;em data-start="2274" data-end="2288"&gt;Lord Bubbles&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/wips/84300"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dark Zonai Tech&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (Zonai retexture mod) — by Aster&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Artist Credits:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2313" data-end="2325"&gt;RaiOuArt (‪&lt;a href="https://bsky.app/profile/raiouart.bsky.social" target="_blank"&gt;Bluesky&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href="https://x.com/RaiOuArt" target="_blank"&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)‬&lt;/strong&gt; — Original concept artwork for the Light Dragon Master Sword&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong data-start="2391" data-end="2402"&gt;ilham45&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;em data-start="2405" data-end="2425"&gt;Yamato (One Piece)&lt;/em&gt; 3D model (hair mesh and textures adapted for this mod)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i class="SelectedElement"&gt;** Mod is made with game version 1.2.1. Use TKMM for all other game versions and to merge your mods.  **&lt;/i&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/dragon_princess_v3_1.zip" type="application/zip"/>
