      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Aug 2025 22:15:35 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe48b65e10.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fe4f03f1d4b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe45f8b37e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe45f52208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe46073fe8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe45f967c2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe459a9b16.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe46050e68.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe583f0fa5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe5847b52a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe5853ca46.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe522db77e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64b5a9d2532b7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe45f42bad.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe4593cf74.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649fe4541d12e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6548150b38343.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6548150c76bab.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6548150cb3708.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6548150d33933.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; DAR 2.4&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Changelog:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Brand New Spawning System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Random Spawning System has been totally reworked, now Enemies can spawn everywhere even inside Caves, Temples and Shrines too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Special Thanks to &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="/members/1676542" data-id="1676542" data-label="Waikuteru" data-type="mention"&gt;@Waikuteru&lt;/a&gt; and his Randomizer mod&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Skip Great Sky Island&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;When starting a new game you can choose to Skip Great Sky Island, you gonna start behind the temple of time ready to go to hyrule, all GSI abilities unlocked, 4 spirit orbs, archaic tunic, legwear and warm graves, 10 apples, 3 chests keys and 10 zonai charges, all 4 shrines and warp points enabled on GSI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Special Thanks to &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="/members/1676542" data-id="1676542" data-label="Waikuteru" data-type="mention"&gt;@Waikuteru&lt;/a&gt; and his Randomizer mod&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;New Locked Chests System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Zonai chests will require one zonai charge to be opened (if you don't have any Small Zonai Charge but you have Large Zonai Charges, you will be asked if you want to use 1 large zonai charge to open the chest).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;New Punitive System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you die or after a blood moon you will lose also 5 large zonai charges in addition to other items.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;New Warp System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Warping cost 10 Small Zonai Charges, if you have more than 3 Large Zonai Zharges, you will be asked what you want to use to warp.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;New Death Screen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you die, the black screen has been removed and enemies will keep on moving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Elemental Stal Bokoblins and Elemental Stal Moblins&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dependig on the region, elemental stals will now spawn, when they gonna be defeated they will cast an elemental explosion (like chuchus). DOTK's elemental bokoblins and moblins will resurrect as elemental stals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Enable/Disable Resurrections option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can choose to Enable or Disable Enemies Resurrections.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;This option is available only in Deluxe Version, Free Version will have Enemies Resurrections Enabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Disable Spawning options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;This can be applied to regular stals, keese and aerocudas, elemental lizalfos, stone pebblit and chuchus.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;These options are available only in Deluxe Version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Large swords can parry' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;All large sword can parry without any fuse item.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;This option is available only in Deluxe Version, in Free Version this option is Enabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Spears can parry' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;All spears can parry without any fuse item.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;This option is available only in Deluxe Version, in Free Version this option is Enabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added No Stagger options to DAR movesets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Attack +75% and -75% options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Defence +75% and -75% options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Better Elemental Armors' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each Ember Armor Pieces will have Hot Weather Attack, Heat Resistance and Burn Resistance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each Charged Armor Pieces will have Stormy Weather Attack, Shock Resistance and Lighting Proof.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each Forstbite Armor Pieces will have Cold Weather Attack, Cold Resistance and Unfreezable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Random Spawning Wooden and Iron Boxes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Wooden and Iron Boxes will randomly spawn everywhere so you gonna have extra help especially if you play with Extreme Punitive Death.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Disable Cooking' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for an extra challenge try this option! You won't be able to cook anymore.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Red Stars will fall from the Sky' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you enable this option, Red Stars will fall from the sky instead of Star Fragment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'Higher Jump' option (so you don't need the TKMM cheat anymore)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;This option is available only in Deluxe Version, in Free Version this option is Enabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'No Fall Damage' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'No Slip when Climbing with Rain' option (wall jumps will slip anyway)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added 'No Gloom Toll on Gloom Weapons' option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Added Slow Bow Stamina options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;You have 5 options now: Default Stamina, 1/4 Stamina Ring Each Shoot, Half Stamina Ring Each Shot, 3/4 Stamina Ring Each Shoot and Full Stamina Ring Each Shoot.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;These options are available only in Deluxe Version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Increased Random Spawning Chests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Random Spawning Chests quantity have been increased.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Fixed No Headshots on Stals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Fixed Upgraded Sages Vow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Higher chance to get armor pieces inside random chests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Mini Bosses will start spawning after you get the Glide&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Random Spawned Chests will give you Random Weapons if you are not using Random Chest options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Removed Blood Effects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Removed Scream Effect and Violet Exposion Effect on Random Spawned Enemies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Random Spawned Enemies won't sleep during nights&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Compatibility Patches&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Updated Challenge Mode Compatibility Patch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now DAR works with the latest Challenge Mode version 1.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Updated Depths of the Kingdom Compatibility Patch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now DAR works with the latest Depths of the Kingdom version 1.1.4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Updated The Second Quest Compatibility Patch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now DAR works with the latest The Second Quest version 1.1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.patreon.com/posts/dark-army-2-4-137123986"&gt;Download Dark Army Resurrection 2.4 - Deluxe - TOTK&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://dark-army-resurrection.fandom.com/wiki/DAR_for_Tears_of_the_Kingdom#How_to_Install"&gt;How to install DAR&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more info check &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://dark-army-resurrection.fandom.com/wiki/DAR_for_Tears_of_the_Kingdom"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dark Army Resurrection TOTK Wiki&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For support join &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FXcrf7cSwP9&amp;amp;follow=true"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dark Army Discord Server&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thanks for all your support!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;What is Dark Army Resurrection?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Dark Army Resurrection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is a mod that aims to create a brand new experience with &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;TOTK&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, adding to the game some original and unique mechanics that will increase the difficulty, furthermore it will introduce a large number of customizable in-game options, simply by interacting with any campfire.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Here are some of the most popular&lt;strong class="SelectedElement"&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;DAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;features:&#13;
&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Random Spawning Enemies System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Enemies will randomly spawn all over the map, the more you progress in the game, the higher will be the enemies rank.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Gambling Chests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - All chests contain 1 to 3 items, some chests can be empty.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Locked Chests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - You need Chests Keys to open chests and Chests Keys are dropped by enemies.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Custom Moveset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Use Double Jump and a brand new Combat System based on Random Combos, Limited Flurry Rush and Easy Perfect Parries.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Enemies Resurrection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Enemies have a chance to resurrect after dying, the higher the enemy rank, the higher the probability to resurrect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Punitive Death and Moon System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - When you die and after a Blood Moon, you will lose all your Rupees and all your Chest Keys.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Extreme Punitive Death and Moon System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - When you die and after a Blood Moon, you will lose all your Items , including weapons and armors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Campfire Options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Change DAR settings in game through campfires.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;TKMM Options&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;(Patreon Only)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Fully customize your gameplay with more than 20 install options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Discord Server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://discord.gg/Xcrf7cSwP9" target="_blank"&gt;Dark Army Resurrection Discord Server&lt;/a&gt; to get full support, updates, beta versions, troubleshooting and more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you like this mod please consider making a &lt;a href="https://paypal.me/miirkuz" target="_blank"&gt;DONATION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://paypal.me/miirkuz" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description>
